sequenceDiagram
  participant User as User
  participant NotionAgent as Notion Agent
  participant Worker as Notion Worker
  participant Notion as Notion API
  participant Libretto as Libretto Cloud

  User->>NotionAgent: run workflow request (in Notion)

  NotionAgent->>Worker: call listWorkflows()
  Worker->>Libretto: POST /v1/workflows/list
  Libretto-->>Worker: workflows
  Worker->>Libretto: POST /v1/workflows/get (workflow names + input/output schemas)
  Libretto-->>Worker: input_schema, output_schema per workflow
  Worker-->>NotionAgent: workflows + input/output schemas

  NotionAgent-->>User: confirm inputs/outputs (per input_schema)
  User-->>NotionAgent: confirmed input values

  NotionAgent->>NotionAgent: pick databaseUrl from Workflows Notion page
  NotionAgent->>Worker: call runWorkflow(workflow_name, databaseUrl, inputs?)
  Worker->>Libretto: POST /v1/jobs/create
  Note over Worker,Libretto: params = { database_id,<br/>...parsed inputs } +<br/>callback URL/secret
  Libretto-->>Worker: job_id
  Worker-->>NotionAgent: job_id

  Libretto->>Libretto: execute workflow

  loop Until run is done
    NotionAgent->>Worker: call checkRun(job_id)
    Worker->>Libretto: POST /v1/jobs/get
    Libretto-->>Worker: job status (running / done / failed)
    Worker-->>NotionAgent: run status
  end

  Libretto->>Worker: POST callback (webhook) with databaseUrl + result
  Worker->>Notion: insert result rows into database
  Notion-->>Worker: pages created

  Worker-->>NotionAgent: run finished
  NotionAgent-->>User: run complete, results inserted into Notion
